{
  "stem": "25809.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I, I went up the roof, but I didn't know that was the end of the-- the wall where I was was the end of, of, of the building.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And as I'm getting up, and I'm trying to grab, all of a sudden I see I was at, I'm at two stories.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I almost-- by, by a hair, I didn't fall down the two stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, I was scared out of my wits that, oh, my god, I'm going to fall here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I hung on for dear life, managed to claw myself up the roof from that little precipice-- I think that's the best way to, to describe it-- climbed on the roof, and hid behind some pipes that were there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Germans got through, but by now it is dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It is dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I did this in the darkness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's why it was so, so scary, because there were-- you couldn't use a flashlight because you would draw attention to yourself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So in, in pitch blackness, I'm stumbling around the roof and put myself flat on the roof so nobody would see me close to some, something that was a little bit-- there are always obstacles on the roof.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So that's where I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, I, I stayed there for, oh, maybe four or five hours and then-- waiting for a signal that, hey, things are OK.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can come back again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, Uncle Kees came, climbed up the precipice said, Jan!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jan!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jan?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I gingerly put my head up and said, I'm here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans are gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I got back in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, we heard about a raid that was taking place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to have Andre get out of the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
